-tr%E1%BA%A1i/poem-H63vGtdfKygZ8uAJ19c51g">Thứ Sa Hà trại - 次沙河寨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Khi%C3%AAn/author-u7e1XRlJeAxu5ZlmUgP9_Q">Ngô Triệu Khiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-tam-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-trmlveecyzF5LgQn_FnFAQ">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tam đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第三段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Di%E1%BB%87u-%C3%9D/T%E1%BB%91ng-Thu%E1%BB%B7-V%C3%A2n-quy-Ng%C3%B4/poem-k9lV2KdO0_9oHbhMPtM0WQ">Tống Thuỷ Vân quy Ngô - 送水雲歸吳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Di%E1%BB%87u-%C3%9D/author-Pc6T9M7s9kAY6e_9xdtzng">Chương Diệu Ý</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-B%C3%A1ch-b%E1%BA%A3o-trang-y%C3%AAu-%C4%91%E1%BB%9Bi/poem-kCject1muTtXwvMMzgq-xQ">Tức sự (Bách bảo trang yêu đới) - 即事（百寶裝腰帶）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
